texts.content: {"text":"1. Biz Nuhni o`z qavmiga, qavmingni ularga \nalamli azob kelishidan avval ogohlantirgin, \ndeb Payg`ambar qilib yubordik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"2. U: «Ey qavmim, albatta, \nmen siz uchun ochiq-oydin ogohlantiruvchiman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"3. Allohga ibodat qilinglar, \nUnga taqvo qilinglar va menga itoat qilinglar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"4. U sizlarning gunohlaringizdan mag`firat qiladir \nva sizni belgilangan ajalgacha qo`yib qo`yadir. \nAgar bilsangiz, albatta, Allohning ajali orqaga surilmaydir», – dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"5. U: «Robbim, men o`z qavmimni \nkechayu kunduz da'vat qildim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"6. Mening chaqirig`im ularda qochishdan \nboshqa narsani ziyoda qilmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"7. Va albatta, qachonki men ularni \nSening mag`firat qilishing uchun chaqirsam, \nular barmoqlarini quloqlariga tiqdilar va kiyimlariga burkanib oldilar, hamda (kofirlikda) sobit bo`ldilar va nihoyatda ulkan takabburlik qildilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,228]}]}

{"text":"8. So`ngra, albatta, men ularni jahriy da'vat qildim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,53]}]}

{"text":"9. So`ngra, albatta, men ularga oshkora \nva yashirin (da'vat) qildim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"10. Bas, o`z Robbingizga istig`for ayting, albatta, \nU gunohlarni ko`plab mag`firat qiluvchidir», dedim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,104]}]}

{"text":"11. «U zot osmondan ustingizga ketma-ket baraka yomg`irini yuboradir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"12. Va sizga molu mulk va bola-chaqa ila madad beradir va sizlarga bog`u rog`lar hamda anhorlarni beradir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,106]}]}

{"text":"13. Sizlarga nima bo`ldiki, Allohning azamatini o`ylab ko`rmaysizlar?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"14. Holbuki, U sizlarni holatma-holat yaratdi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,46]}]}

{"text":"15. Alloh yetti osmonni qandoq qilib tabaqama-tabaqa yaratib qo`yganini ko`rmadingizmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"16. Va ular ichida oyni nur va quyoshni chiroq qilib qo`yganini ko`rmadingizmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"17. Va Alloh sizlarni yerdan o`stirib chiqaradir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,49]}]}

{"text":"18. So`ngra sizlarni unga qaytaradir va \nyana chiqaradir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,57]}]}

{"text":"19. Va Alloh sizlarga yerni gilamdek to`shab qo`ydi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,52]}]}

{"text":"20. Unda siz keng yo`llardan yurishingiz uchun», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,54]}]}

{"text":"21. Nuh: «Ey Robbim, albatta, ular menga isyon qildilar va moli, bola-chaqasi xusrondan boshqani ziyoda qilmaganga ergashdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,127]}]}

{"text":"22. Va nihoyatda ulkan makr qildilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,37]}]}

{"text":"23. Va ular: «Olihalaringizni hech tark qilmanglar, 
va, albatta, Vaddni ham, Suva'ni ham, 
Yag`usni ham, Ya'uqni ham va Nasrni ham 
tark qilmang», dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"24. Darhaqiqat, ular ko`plarini adashtirdi. Va Sen zolimlarga zalolatdan boshqani ziyoda qilma», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,102]}]}

{"text":"25. Ular xatolari tufayli g`arq qilindilar, bas, olovga kiritildilar. Bas, o`zlariga Allohdan o`zga yordamchi topa olmadilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,125]}]}

{"text":"26. Va Nuh: «Ey Robbim, yer yuzida kofirlardan birorta ham harakatlanuvchini qo`ymagin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"27. Albatta, sen ularni tek qo`ysang, bandalaringni adashtiradilar va fojiru kofirdan boshqa tug`maslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,104]}]}

{"text":"28. Robbim, meni mag`firat qilgin, mening ota-onamni ham va uyimga mo`min bo`lib kirganlarni va mo`minlaru mo`minalarni ham. Va zolimlarga halokatdan o`zga narsani ziyoda qilma», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,184]}]}

{"text":" إِنَّآ أَرْسَلْنَا نُوحًا إِلَىٰ قَوْمِهِۦٓ أَنْ أَنذِرْ قَوْمَكَ مِن قَبْلِ أَن يَأْتِيَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,112]}]}

{"text":"قَالَ يَٰقَوْمِ إِنِّى لَكُمْ نَذِيرٌۭ مُّبِينٌ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"أَنِ ٱعْبُدُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَٱتَّقُوهُ وَأَطِيعُونِ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"يَغْفِرْ لَكُم مِّن ذُنُوبِكُمْ وَيُؤَخِّرْكُمْ إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلٍۢ مُّسَمًّى ۚ \nإِنَّ أَجَلَ ٱللَّهِ إِذَا جَآءَ لَا يُؤَخَّرُ ۖ لَوْ كُنتُمْ تَعْلَمُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,151]}]}

{"text":"قَالَ رَبِّ إِنِّى دَعَوْتُ قَوْمِى لَيْلًۭا وَنَهَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"فَلَمْ يَزِدْهُمْ دُعَآءِىٓ إِلَّا فِرَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,45]}]}

{"text":"وَإِنِّى كُلَّمَا دَعَوْتُهُمْ لِتَغْفِرَ لَهُمْ جَعَلُوٓا۟ أَصَٰبِعَهُمْ فِىٓ ءَاذَانِهِمْ \nوَٱسْتَغْشَوْا۟ ثِيَابَهُمْ وَأَصَرُّوا۟ وَٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟ ٱسْتِكْبَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,165]}]}

{"text":"ثُمَّ إِنِّى دَعَوْتُهُمْ جِهَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,35]}]}

{"text":"ثُمَّ إِنِّىٓ أَعْلَنتُ لَهُمْ وَأَسْرَرْتُ لَهُمْ إِسْرَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"فَقُلْتُ ٱسْتَغْفِرُوا۟ رَبَّكُمْ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ غَفَّارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"يُرْسِلِ ٱلسَّمَآءَ عَلَيْكُم مِّدْرَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"وَيُمْدِدْكُم بِأَمْوَٰلٍۢ وَبَنِينَ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ جَنَّٰتٍۢ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ أَنْهَٰرًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,94]}]}

{"text":"مَّا لَكُمْ لَا تَرْجُونَ لِلَّهِ وَقَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"وَقَدْ خَلَقَكُمْ أَطْوَارًا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,28]}]}

{"text":"أَلَمْ تَرَوْا۟ كَيْفَ خَلَقَ ٱللَّهُ سَبْعَ سَمَٰوَٰتٍۢ طِبَاقًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"وَجَعَلَ ٱلْقَمَرَ فِيهِنَّ نُورًۭا وَجَعَلَ ٱلشَّمْسَ سِرَاجًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"وَٱللَّهُ أَنۢبَتَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْأَرْضِ نَبَاتًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"ثُمَّ يُعِيدُكُمْ فِيهَا وَيُخْرِجُكُمْ إِخْرَاجًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"وَٱللَّهُ جَعَلَ لَكُمُ ٱلْأَرْضَ بِسَاطًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"لِّتَسْلُكُوا۟ مِنْهَا سُبُلًۭا فِجَاجًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,41]}]}

{"text":"قَالَ نُوحٌۭ رَّبِّ إِنَّهُمْ عَصَوْنِى وَٱتَّبَعُوا۟ مَن لَّمْ يَزِدْهُ مَالُهُۥ وَوَلَدُهُۥٓ إِلَّا خَسَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"وَمَكَرُوا۟ مَكْرًۭا كُبَّارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,31]}]}

{"text":"وَقَالُوا۟ لَا تَذَرُنَّ ءَالِهَتَكُمْ وَلَا تَذَرُنَّ وَدًّۭا وَلَا سُوَاعًۭا وَلَا يَغُوثَ وَيَعُوقَ وَنَسْرًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,113]}]}

{"text":"وَقَدْ أَضَلُّوا۟ كَثِيرًۭا ۖ وَلَا تَزِدِ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ إِلَّا ضَلَٰلًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"مِّمَّا خَطِيٓـَٰٔتِهِمْ أُغْرِقُوا۟ فَأُدْخِلُوا۟ نَارًۭا فَلَمْ يَجِدُوا۟ لَهُم مِّن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَنصَارًۭا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"وَقَالَ نُوحٌۭ رَّبِّ لَا تَذَرْ عَلَى ٱلْأَرْضِ مِنَ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ دَيَّارًا","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,77]}]}
